{"tid":1216761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下大家拖喼搭地鐵過金鐘會唔會俾警察逗","createTime":"2019-06-13T10:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T18:02:35.000Z","uid":7628,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"af952d7f364e778054e523b7a47ed950c93c73e8","tid":1216761,"uid":7628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:56:14.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，小弟最近換咗個新喼所以想掉咗個舊喼。我屋企附近冇垃圾收集站我又唔想掉去大廈垃圾房咁仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n聽朋友講金鐘站附近有個垃圾收集站幾大下，而我星期一又會咁啱經過金鐘喎。所以諗住搭地鐵再行過去金鐘廊垃圾收集站囉，我好驚俾警察逗，我一緊張就會唔記得啲嘢，我怕到時我唔記得個喼解鎖密碼俾唔到佢check。點算!<br />\n<br />\n到底掉唔掉去金鐘廊垃圾收集站好呢，希望大家俾俾意見小弟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84347c41795958e091d8843a1bacd3faf88554b8","tid":1216761,"uid":7628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:56:31.000Z","msg":"真心一問!"},{"pid":"f8f7895d645eeafff3cce0df990401fae8618bdf","tid":1216761,"uid":51760,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:57:13.000Z","msg":"唔清楚 <br />\n但試下講埋普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"525380eb2494040e262cf95915aa8ee3eccd6028","tid":1216761,"uid":7628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:57:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c411ab062bacd453bdfe93d0ee8b9f0f91d6391","tid":1216761,"uid":7628,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:58:21.000Z","msg":"大家有冇舊喼要掉啊，不如一齊去金鐘掉啦"},{"pid":"b6863861a7a81ef265d8e1b303521caa14f7a53c","tid":1216761,"uid":258328,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:00:38.000Z","msg":"約人交收賣gip比人都唔得咩on9"},{"pid":"5a6df83333243fcee3cb17bf4ae79a4fd70e7e67","tid":1216761,"uid":7628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0